WEBVTT

00:00:28.848 --> 00:00:31.748
dok gledaš kako ćeš napraviti
savršenu fotografiju.

00:00:31.772 --> 00:00:34.302
Sve je bilo u redu dok...

00:00:34.326 --> 00:00:35.891
nije prestalo biti.

00:00:35.915 --> 00:00:39.017
Nešto stvarno nije bilo u redu.

00:00:39.552 --> 00:00:41.388
Povukla sam ruku,

00:00:41.412 --> 00:00:44.054
a duge, crne bodlje morskog ježinca

00:00:44.078 --> 00:00:45.678
virile su iz moje rukavice,

00:00:45.702 --> 00:00:47.801
odnosno prolazile kroz cijelu moju šaku.

00:00:48.344 --> 00:00:50.356
To nije dobro.

00:00:50.380 --> 00:00:53.169
Kada vam nešto prođe kroz šaku,

00:00:53.169 --> 00:00:55.103
to je uvijek loše,

00:00:55.127 --> 00:00:59.307
ali u ovom slučaju, 
morski ježevi imaju otrov koji,

00:00:59.331 --> 00:01:00.924
ako ste ikad imali posla s njima,